sellerCard.oneLiner: Quality Conscious Full Stack Web Developer
sellerCard.description: Passionate Full Stack Developer skilled in PHP Laravel, React, Next js, Python, Django, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap and Tailwind CSS. I Specialize in creating seamless, visually stunning websites by blending functionality with finess. From building robust databases to dynamic API's, I turn idea into reality. Let's elevate your project with tech expertise and commitment to excellence. Ready to bring your web dreams to life? Let's make it happen!,

description.content:
Welcome to my Gig


I am an experienced web developer more than a 4 years of experience in website development, I bring expertise in building custom websites and dynamic web applications. Proficient in HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, Tailwind CSS, React JS, Next Js, PHP, Laravel and Nodejs jQuery, I ensure each project is both visually captivating and functionally robust.


I specialize in turning designs into fully responsive, user-friendly website that prioritize seamless interaction and exceptional user experiences. Whether you need to develop a project from the ground up or enhance an existing one, Im committed to delivering innovative and high-quality solutions tailored to your goals.



Frontend Services

  1. HTML (Hyper Text Markup Language)
  2. CSS (Cascading Style Sheet)
  3. JAVASCRIPT
  4. BOOTSTRAP
  5. Tailwind CSS
  6. SCSS (Sassy Cascading Style Sheets)
  7. JQUERY
  8. REACT JS
  9. NEXT JS


Expertise (Backend)

  1. Python
  2. Nodejs
  3. PHP
  4. Laravel
  5. Mysql
  6. API


Feel free to ask me if you have any queries or questions would like to consultant with your requirements with my experience


Looking forward to working with you


Thank you

Sajjad Ali
